.TH FB2LESS 1 "30 April 2026" "0.8.2" "fb2less manual"
.SH NAME
fb2less \- Advanced terminal-based eBook reader
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fb2less
[\fIFILE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B fb2less
is a terminal eBook reader for FB2, EPUB, and TXT formats, written in Python using the curses library.
It features ZIP archive support, footnote viewing, auto-scrolling, chapter and percentage navigation, and an advanced bookmark manager. Users can customize background, text, and header colors, text width, and border types. All settings are saved individually for each book. If \fIFILE\fR is not specified, the program opens the last read book from history.
.SH OPTIONS
.IP "\-h, \-\-help"
Show help message and exit.
.IP "\-v, \-\-version"
Show version information and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD COMMANDS
.TP 20
.IP "K"
Switch interface language (EN/RU).
.IP "j, Down / k, Up"
Scroll text one line down or up.
.IP "d / u"
Scroll half a page forward or backward.
.IP "PgUp, Left"
Scroll one page backward.
.IP "Space, PgDn, Right"
Scroll one page forward.
.IP "[, ]"
Jump to the previous or next chapter.
.IP "p"
Jump to a specific percentage.
.IP "i"
Show book metadata and annotation.
.IP "Z"
Scan directory. Recursively searches for books, updates library, and removes missing files.
.IP "L"
Open library. Shows a list of previously opened books with search support (/ key).
.IP "Del / d"
Remove the selected entry from the library (does not delete the actual file).
.IP "Enter"
Open the selected book in the library or table of contents.
.IP "t"
Open interactive Table of Contents.
.IP "f"
Cycle through footnotes on the current page.
.IP "/"
Search for text within the book.
.IP "n / N"
Jump to the next or previous search match.
.IP "m"
Set a bookmark at the current position.
.IP "M"
Open the Bookmark Manager to jump to or delete existing bookmarks.
.IP "a"
Toggle auto-scrolling.
.IP "s / S"
Increase or decrease auto-scroll speed.
.IP "c / b / v"
Change text (c), background (b), or header (v) colors.
.IP "B"
Toggle border type: window-based, text-based, or none.
.IP "e"
Page flip mode: instant or animated (3 variants).
.IP "\-, ="
Decrease or increase text block width.
.IP "h"
Show built-in help window.
.IP "q"
Exit and save current position.
.SH FILES
.IP "~/.fb2less_history"
JSON file containing reading history, bookmarks, and per-book settings.
.SH AUTHOR
Written by measles.
